# Copy to secrets.env in this directory (gitignored) for local Docker Compose and the CLI.
# Do not commit real values. Which keys to set (tokens, local API, etc.): docs/cli.md
#
# Optional overrides (otherwise auto-generated under SELLERCLAW_DATA_DIR/secrets.json):
